text: Arsanjan County () is a county in Fars Province in Iran. The capital of the county is Arsanjan.Gitashenasi Province Atlas of Iran اطلس گیتاشناسی استان‌های ایران At the 2006 census, the county's population was 40,916, in 9,800 families. The county has one district: the Central District. The county has one city: Arsanjan. == References == Category:Counties in Fars Province
title: Arsanjan County
